{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124339071142072320419507.jpeg/7rI42B2LCeeTGFINke3C4PaNhY-jQDxmqB0KFKgdChQ\" alt=\"荷李活道一間店舖報稱失古董馬。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>荷李活道一間店舖報稱失古董馬。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><p>現場消息稱，店舖有物品正拿走展覽，報稱失竊的古董馬，未知是否被拿去，職員正核實中。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124339068289814528351792.jpeg/Vn2BX4EKww1Gn4oBA19j38ka9YDGMLHBu36PV7t-j1c\" alt=\"店舖的古董馬報稱被偷。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>店舖的古董馬報稱被偷。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124339065164926976207194.jpeg/fAtmAs5F6ugZTIA-wrATh3WjGfVkeLutgMYRwIDGEcA\" alt=\"店舖的古董馬報稱被偷。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>店舖的古董馬報稱被偷。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-24T05:47:19.881842+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":99,"images":3,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}